    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's totally spotless inside and out. If you're looking for your dream ride that's been loved and pampered, this is definitely the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
