      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers linear power with surgical precision. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and exit speeds. The chassis is structurally flawless, with no signs of subframe fatigue, ensuring the original torsional rigidity remains intact. Every bushing, damper, and suspension link remains in peak operational condition, preserving the communicative steering feel and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist who values mechanical purity and drivetrain longevity.",
